Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.37,0:00:04.94,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just as water flows without shape and wind blows without form,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.94,0:00:06.94,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}no case can stop you from deducing the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.94,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today, Kogorō gets a huge scare at a hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:10.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and Ran's also acting pretty weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:12.35,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:13.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:16.45,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.56,0:01:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm gonna be away a little longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:48.15,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Geez, what've you been doing?\NEverybody at school is worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:49.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.53,0:01:53.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'I'm on a really tough case', right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.66,0:01:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry, Shin'ichi! I have to go or I'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.54,0:01:59.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:02.27,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Bye! It's getting colder, so be careful so you don't catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:03.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:11.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I don't know why, but Ran's been acting weird these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.32,0:02:18.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's kind of cold over the phone, and she doesn't cry 'Shin'ichi! Shin'ichi!' like she used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:22.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But the weirdest thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:25.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, I'm going out for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.44,0:02:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dinner's on the table. Warm it up in the microwave before you eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:32.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.40,0:02:38.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...is that she goes out every afternoon and only comes back late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:41.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She {\i1}claims{\i0} she's got extra training for the karate club tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:43.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But it doesn't really fit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.31,0:02:45.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She always looks so... {\i1}happy{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:55.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then, one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.74,0:02:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You've been going to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.34,0:03:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We're about to get the results of my tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:05.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sick, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe. I've been feeling very tired lately.{Kogorō's in saa mode}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.88,0:03:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've probably been drinking too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly! You didn't have to pick us up from school for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:17.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The doctor told me on the phone\Nto bring my closest relatives along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.02,0:03:26.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kogorō Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:42.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry about this,\Nbut you have six months...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.00,0:03:44.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you do this to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suddenly telling me that\NI only have six months to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:51.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I have that serious a disease, you should've told me earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:53.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a doctor, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Serious disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I was trying to say was that you have to refrain from drinking alcohol for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:01.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alcohol?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:07.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to your blood test, you've got a case of alcohol-induced cirrhosis of the liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Though it's not too serious yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:13.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.03,0:04:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you scared me, Dr. Araide!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You made me bring my family and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:26.06,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yoshiteru Araide (51)\NLocal Practitioner
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:23.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,With patients like you, who like to drink so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:26.05,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,cooperation from the family is essential.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:28.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just cut down on the amount\Nyou drink each day, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! I won't let him drink a single drop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.73,0:04:36.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got a phone call from Sugita{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She wants you to make a house call.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.85,0:04:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's one tough patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.62,0:04:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just a gastric ulcer,\Nbut she's so worried about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:52.09,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Patient? Yeah, right. More like mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.83,0:04:52.09,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yōko Araide (46)\NYoshiteru's wife
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.17,0:04:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.41,0:04:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait a moment. I'm sure he'll be off the phone soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:00.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:04.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I use your toilet?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The public toilet seems to be broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.73,0:05:10.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:13.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the way, I turned right at the end of the corridor, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:18.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means the examination room must be right up ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.06,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This house is so big...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... I wasn't looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.50,0:05:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. It was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here. That should be all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.95,0:05:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.95,0:05:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Mouri's daughter. He's seeing Dr. Araide.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:54.22,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm the doctor's son, Tomoaki.\NI help my father out here at his clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.22,0:05:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm going off to work at a hospital in Aomori starting next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:54.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Tomoaki Araide (25)\NYoshiteru's son / Doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When are you going to get used to working here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And after you begged me to hire you as a maid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.46,0:06:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know getting too riled-up is bad for your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:20.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen up! Screw up again, and you're fired!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.99,0:06:23.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Ugh! I've had enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.18,0:06:26.12,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Hikaru Yasumoto (22)\NHousemaid
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember to stay away from alcohol if you want a long and happy life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You even have the same name as that other Kogorō Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:40.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't you heard of him?\NHe's a great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.15,0:06:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. You see, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.31,0:06:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You're really him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.42,0:06:49.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.62,0:06:55.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, when I saw your name, I did wonder, but I didn't expect that you were really him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.55,0:07:01.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had me fooled completely,\Npretending to have no medical knowledge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.81,0:07:05.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you join me for dinner tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.25,0:07:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can exchange ideas about forensic medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.70,0:07:09.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.08,0:07:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-We can't! I've got homework,\Nand Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} has karate practice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.33,0:07:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:18.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine. Since they're inviting, we might as well go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can skip practice once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:28.85,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,'Araide Clinic —\hClosed for the day'
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:26.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it. Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.26,0:07:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You graduated at the top of your class at Tohto Medical School, Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.89,0:07:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was lucky, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.41,0:07:41.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, how about you marry my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.12,0:07:42.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.17,0:07:45.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think you'd make a fine couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.71,0:07:54.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful! The {\i1}chawanmushi{\i0} is hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.27,0:07:55.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.67,0:07:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you going to make arrangements for your class reunion tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right! I have to call Masae!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:09.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{You're free to marry her whenever you like!}Hey, if you ever think it over, let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We could be like Holmes and Watson!\NTogether, we can solve any mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think I'll pass on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure a detective and a doctor would make a good pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.13,0:08:27.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The real job of a doctor isn't to find the murderer by performing an autopsy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but to save the victim from death in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know which one would be Holmes though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:38.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-nee{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:40.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:45.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's taking your husband so long.\NHis clinic should've closed by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's taking a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:58.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That man always takes a bath before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.46,0:09:01.19,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mitsu Araide (74)\NTomoaki's Grandmother
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:01.19,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He dirties the water for everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma! Don't talk like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:08.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, traditionally the breadwinner of the family enters the bath first.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:11.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Breadwinner, my foot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.77,0:09:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the one who married into my family, so he's got no right to put on airs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:21.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only blood relation\NI've got left in this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:25.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you're leaving home next month...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're practically {\i1}telling{\i0} me to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.08,0:09:32.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, what about dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{You strangers can eat together!}I have no interest in eating around strangers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.48,0:09:40.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't let her bother you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:46.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma's been in a bad mood since Dad changed the bath and toilet to Western style.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.43,0:09:47.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Western style?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:49.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.18,0:09:54.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was very annoyed when he replaced our antique cypress bath with a modern tub and shower curtain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.64,0:09:57.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She says it's a dishonour against the house's tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.50,0:10:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, she sure is an energetic old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, a blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's just this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The lights are on next door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.32,0:10:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, I think there's a flashlight\Nin that drawer over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.61,0:10:20.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go take a look at the circuit breaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.11,0:10:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Watch your step, Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.18,0:10:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.70,0:10:32.31,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:33.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've got a blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, is it raining?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.27,0:10:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.18,0:10:49.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:10:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry! I mistook you for Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:03.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:08.97,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And about the fee...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. I think ¥30,000 is too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:12.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are the lights back on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Silly girl! Can't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think we should check on Dad in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he's upset about all the lights going off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:22.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm worried about his heart too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.93,0:11:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:25.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:27.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:29.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What caused the blackout, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:30.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:34.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could've been a short-circuit, or too much electricity being used at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That came from the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.64,0:11:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.29,0:12:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.04,0:12:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't touch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.26,0:12:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you do, you'll get an electric shock too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.14,0:12:11.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Electric shock?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:16.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:22.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's an extension cord\Nconnected to this electric razor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:26.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll try to resuscitate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:29.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mother, go get the drip with the cardiotonic!{cat: Go get the heart medicine!}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.13,0:12:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.03,0:12:31.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:33.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and call the police, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.91,0:12:37.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:46.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It looks like he was shocked when that electric cord fell in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.69,0:12:51.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He could've been using that mirror over the bathtub to shave.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:54.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why would he shave in the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:57.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.22,0:12:58.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.88,0:13:04.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to report that Yoshiteru Araide{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} has passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:08.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He did have a weak heart to begin with...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:11.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-This... This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In what state did you find Yoshiteru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:20.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was slumped in the bathtub\Nwith his head facing this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why'd he use an electric razor in the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.46,0:13:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a habit of my husband's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:30.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He always did it while keeping his guests waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even got a mirror that wouldn't fog up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:39.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wasn't it strange for him to take a bath and keep his guests waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.26,0:13:44.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad loved taking baths. He always took a bath in the morning and before dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.74,0:13:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He thought it was important\Nfor doctors to keep clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He deserved it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:53.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This was divine retribution\Nfor not listening to Chiaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:58.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiaki decided to punish him from above!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:13:59.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's Chiaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother. She died in a car accident four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:12.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She always told him not to use the electric razor in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said it was dangerous to use it with the cord attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:17.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Yōko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:21.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm his second wife.\NWe got married two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chiaki and I were in the same\Nclass at nursing school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and she often talked about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:32.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you stand up to shave yourself in front of the mirror,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.13,0:14:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the socket of this extension cord\Ncomes right to the edge of the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:39.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This sure is risky...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.37,0:14:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were all of you\Nwhen the blackout occurred?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.54,0:14:50.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My mother-in-law wasn't, but I saw her climb up the stairs at the other end of the corridor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.46,0:14:55.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then Yoshiteru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was using the electric razor in the bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.77,0:15:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and accidentally pulled the cord into the bathtub, causing a deadly electric shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A simple accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:04.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:12.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! No fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm so confused, I've got a splitting headache!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.69,0:15:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.38,0:15:21.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man who died was shaving himself standing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was pretending to be him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:26.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then when he felt the shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.33,0:15:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he should've fallen over like Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},\Nwith his head on this side, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that man's head was facing the other way! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:35.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.75,0:15:38.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Hey, the kid's got a point.}That could've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While Yoshiteru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was shaving himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.83,0:15:50.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he noticed that the cord was\Nabout to fall into the bath,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:53.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so he turned around to pick it up, but ended up pulling it into the bath instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:59.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he happened to touch the handrail, electricity flowed through him with a shock,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:02.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he fell into the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:04.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like that, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.63,0:16:08.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10Not bad, old man.}Not too shabby, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:12.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't play with that razor, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it an important piece of evidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Play? I'm just holding it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then was it you, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.15,0:16:22.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? I didn't mess with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the man from forensics?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I just took photos...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:31.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weird. Then who could've played around with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.12,0:16:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The razor's switched off! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.31,0:16:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, it's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:47.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If this man died of an electric shock while shaving, the razor should be on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Takagi must've pushed the power switch when he fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.54,0:16:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:17:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? I thought we unplugged that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.07,0:17:03.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did. I'm holding the plug now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.01,0:17:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! This is a rechargeable shaver!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:10.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then why was it turned off?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.31,0:17:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{It wasn't on when you found the body, was it?}Nobody touched it since you found the body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.52,0:17:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.94,0:17:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's the sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.09,0:17:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody didn't want the sound of the shaver to be heard!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.03,0:17:24.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who{\i0} didn't want {\i1}who{\i0} to hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:28.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{How would I know? I'm just a dumb kid!}Beats me! I'm just making guesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.16,0:17:34.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe somebody wanted to sneak the cord in the tub while Yoshiteru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was taking his bath
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.11,0:17:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,without catching his attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:38.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If somebody did that, he'd have noticed it even without the noise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.82,0:17:47.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And everybody has an alibi during the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, when the light came on, it went off again for a moment before coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you're the one who reset the breaker, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.52,0:17:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.98,0:18:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you by any chance flip it twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:06.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.11,0:18:08.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I might have flipped the wrong switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.01,0:18:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A different breaker shut off,\Nso I quickly flipped it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, the second time the breaker jumped, could it have...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer could create some sort of timer to cause a blackout,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then use the opportunity to sneak into the bathroom and drop the cord into the bathtub.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then any one of those four...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...could have killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.60,0:18:40.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you whispering?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.17,0:18:45.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Never mind! I was wondering if we could hear what you were doing during the blackout.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:48.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't we just tell you our alibis?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.91,0:18:53.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you saying there's a murderer among us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.72,0:18:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We just want to be sure, that's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you were on the phone the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:01.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.92,0:19:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From before the blackout to the time the lights turned back on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.29,0:19:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was talking on the phone next to the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was talking to my friend Masae about our class reunion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:18.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and my call waiting went off too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.10,0:19:21.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the person on the other end just hung up without saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.58,0:19:23.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi! Go check that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.04,0:19:29.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the blackout, I dug out the torch and handed it to Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that, I was in the kitchen the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you prove that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.17,0:19:36.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Er, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was here the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.12,0:19:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the point when Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} went to reset the breaker,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.80,0:19:47.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I grabbed onto Tomoaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} the whole time. I was scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.88,0:19:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:57.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I? I mistook him for Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, Mitsu{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}. Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.83,0:20:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the lights went off, I'd just finished climbing the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.52,0:20:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I groped my way back to my room upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when the lights went on, you came back down the stairs to the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.03,0:20:21.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt a presence just as I was about to go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.29,0:20:24.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like someone was just outside my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone else may have\Nbeen inside the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.89,0:20:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.84,0:20:34.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I followed the presence downstairs and discovered...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.64,0:20:35.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.92,0:20:38.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was only the sound of rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.31,0:20:40.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.09,0:20:44.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally, Hikaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:45.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.63,0:20:49.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I went to reset the circuit breaker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:53.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not used to this house yet,\Nso I got lost at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:56.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you didn't see anyone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.40,0:20:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. Nobody.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:05.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wondering why you kept touching your arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:12.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still put up with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:13.72,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A burn mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Can I go down to the clinic to treat her wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:22.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure. But go with the\Ndetective waiting outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want to keep watch, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.02,0:21:28.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and one more thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:34.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who left this house today, from 5 to 7 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:35.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where did you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.97,0:21:38.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I coach the high school basketball team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their coach used to teach me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he broke a bone and asked me if I could take over for him until he recovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.83,0:21:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A doctor {\i1}and{\i0} a sports coach?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe me, ask Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.81,0:21:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The team I'm coaching is at Teitan High School, the same school she goes to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.58,0:22:02.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know Tabuchi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r},\Nthe basketball coach, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:03.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.70,0:22:06.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.51,0:22:10.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Is that why Ran went out to karate practice at school every evening?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:13.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.31,0:22:16.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It couldn't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:49.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.22,0:23:53.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you go take a look at the breaker?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.41,0:23:54.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.21,0:23:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why another blackout?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.17,0:24:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, that man said he was running an experiment in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.56,0:24:05.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.20,0:24:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the killer, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.52,0:24:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: 'The Blind Spot in the Darkness (Part II)'!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.56,0:24:20.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Burn wound!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.91,0:24:21.63,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.63,0:24:23.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Not good... Ran's feelings are...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.55,0:24:25.55,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Huh? Were you there, Shin'ichi?
